# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:9
translate spanish day1_f277ad4a:

    # "THE NEXT MORNING"
    "A LA MAÑANA SIGUIENTE"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:14
translate spanish day1_140f51d4:

    # "I am woken by a knock on my door."
    "Me despierta un golpe en la puerta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:15
translate spanish day1_d72509a6:

    # pc "Yeah?"
    pc "¿Sí?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:16
translate spanish day1_1b92974a:

    # sp "I made breakfast. You have a little time to eat before you need to go register for school."
    sp "He hecho el desayuno. Tienes un rato para comer antes de ir a matricularte en la universidad."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:17
translate spanish day1_836b3b51:

    # "I look around, disoriented for a moment. It takes a bit for me to realize where I am – in my bedroom, at home."
    "Miro a mi alrededor, desorientado por un momento. Me cuesta un poco darme cuenta de dónde estoy: en mi dormitorio, en casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:18
translate spanish day1_71d014f3:

    # "I had fallen asleep hard the night before and didn't wake up at all throughout the night. Unusual for me."
    "La noche anterior me había quedado profundamente dormido y no me desperté en toda la noche. Algo inusual en mí."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:19
translate spanish day1_84e65c22:

    # pc "Okay, thanks. I'll be down in a few minutes. "
    pc "Vale, gracias. Bajaré en unos minutos. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:20
translate spanish day1_9f064b85:

    # sp "I have to get to work. I won't be home until late tonight. Have a good day."
    sp "Tengo que irme a trabajar. No volveré a casa hasta tarde esta noche. Que tengas un buen día."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:21
translate spanish day1_790762a2:

    # "I crawl out of bed, feeling pretty good. The clock on my nightstand says it is 9:15. "
    "Me levanto de la cama, sintiéndome bastante bien. El reloj de mi mesita de noche marca las 9:15. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:23
translate spanish day1_cdbaf5ac:

    # "I give a little knock on the bathroom door to make sure that Suzy isn't in there, then walk in, empty my bladder, and smooth out my bedhead a bit. "
    "Doy un golpecito a la puerta del baño para asegurarme de que Suzy no está dentro, luego entro, hago mis necesidades y me aliso un poco el pelo revuelto. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:26
translate spanish day1_b945239f:

    # "Then I throw a shirt on and head downstairs, where I can smell pancakes before I even get to the bottom step. "
    "Después me pongo una camiseta y bajo las escaleras, donde ya puedo oler las tortitas antes incluso de llegar al último escalón. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:29
translate spanish day1_e9b07aab:

    # "Suzy is already sitting at the table eating. "
    "Suzy ya está sentada a la mesa comiendo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:30
translate spanish day1_bb51adeb:

    # ss "The pancakes are under the foil in there. "
    ss "Las tortitas están ahí debajo del papel de aluminio. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:31
translate spanish day1_b53f8364:

    # pc "Thanks. "
    pc "Gracias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:34
translate spanish day1_d1f6cf0b:

    # "I go to the kitchen and put two pancakes on my plate along with a pad of butter and a little syrup, then I walk back to the dining room and sit across from Suzy."
    "Voy a la cocina y pongo dos tortitas en mi plato junto con un trozo de mantequilla y un poco de sirope, luego vuelvo al comedor y me siento frente a Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:35
translate spanish day1_4025fcb1:

    # ss "She hasn't cooked breakfast in forever. I'm not sure why you're getting the special treatment, but I'm happy for the pancakes. "
    ss "Hace una eternidad que no prepara el desayuno. No sé muy bien por qué te dan un trato especial, pero me alegro por las tortitas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:36
translate spanish day1_7a4286af:

    # pc "Careful. It almost sounded like you were saying that you're happy I'm back. "
    pc "Cuidado. Casi parecía que decías que te alegras de que haya vuelto. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:38
translate spanish day1_7edc6e89:

    # ss "Are you back? Or are you just going to leave us again? "
    ss "¿Has vuelto? ¿O vas a volver a dejarnos? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:39
translate spanish day1_62e06f66:

    # pc "I'm back. Seriously. I'm not going anywhere. "
    pc "He vuelto. En serio. No me voy a ir a ningún sitio. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:41
translate spanish day1_d9d7dc1b:

    # "Suzy scoffs, unconvinced. "
    "Suzy se burla, sin estar convencida. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:42
translate spanish day1_aefae29f:

    # ss "We'll see. "
    ss "Ya veremos. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:43
translate spanish day1_7a69dfe1:

    # pc "I promise, [sis]. Really. I'm not going back. You're going to have to deal with me for a long time. "
    pc "Te lo prometo, [sis]. De verdad. No voy a volver. Vas a tener que aguantarme durante mucho tiempo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:45
translate spanish day1_1d417bec:

    # "Suzy smiles, side-eyeing me."
    "Suzy sonríe, mirándome de reojo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:46
translate spanish day1_85c4dd14:

    # ss "Great. "
    ss "Genial. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:47
translate spanish day1_51120906:

    # ss "I'm going to go get ready. Be ready at 10, okay? "
    ss "Voy a prepararme. Tenlo todo listo a las 10, ¿vale? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:48
translate spanish day1_fc94baf7:

    # pc "You got it. And thanks for being my ride for today. "
    pc "De acuerdo. Y gracias por llevarme hoy. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:49
translate spanish day1_971e823a:

    # ss "Yeah, just don't make it a habit. "
    ss "Sí, pero que no se convierta en una costumbre. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:52
translate spanish day1_9f8d7627:

    # "She stands up and grabs her plate, heading towards the kitchen. "
    "Se levanta, coge su plato y se dirige a la cocina. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:53
translate spanish day1_e0bc8a6d:

    # pc "Hey, [sis]? "
    pc "Oye, [sis]? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:54
translate spanish day1_4339758a:

    # ss "What? "
    ss "¿Qué? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:55
translate spanish day1_13248281:

    # pc "When's trash day? "
    pc "¿Cuándo es el día de la basura? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:56
translate spanish day1_33714114:

    # ss "How the hell should I know? Friday maybe? "
    ss "¿Cómo demonios voy a saberlo? ¿El viernes, quizá? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:57
translate spanish day1_c4b1d53a:

    # pc "So today?"
    pc "¿Entonces hoy?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:58
translate spanish day1_751e4576:

    # ss "Maybe?"
    ss "¿Quizá?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:59
translate spanish day1_87647b2c:

    # "I think about asking her to help me take the trash out, but then decide against it. Easier to just do it by myself. "
    "Pienso en pedirle que me ayude a sacar la basura, pero luego decido no hacerlo. Es más fácil hacerlo yo solo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:60
translate spanish day1_775dea27:

    # "I eat quickly, scarfing down all the delicious pancakes. Then I put my plate into the sink before grabbing the kitchen trash and carrying it outside to the trash bins. "
    "Como rápido, devorando todos los deliciosos panqueques. Luego dejo el plato en el fregadero antes de coger la bolsa de basura de la cocina y llevarla fuera a los contenedores. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:63
translate spanish day1_f4cc524d:

    # "It takes two trips to move the trash cans to the curb and I get them there just as the garbage man is driving up to the house to pick them up. "
    "Tardo dos viajes en sacar los cubos a la acera y los dejo allí justo cuando el basurero se acerca en su camión para recogerlos. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:64
translate spanish day1_3e905c90:

    # "He gives me a wave and a smile before I realize that I had never put on pants and am standing outside in my boxers. Oops."
    "Me saluda con la mano y me sonríe antes de que me dé cuenta de que no me he puesto los pantalones y estoy ahí fuera en calzoncillos. ¡Ups!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:66
translate spanish day1_aa42da63:

    # "I rush back inside and upstairs, throwing on some clothes from my suitcase and making a quick trip to the bathroom to make myself a bit more presentable. "
    "Corro de vuelta al interior y subo las escaleras, me pongo algo de ropa de la maleta y voy rápidamente al baño para arreglarme un poco. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:67
translate spanish day1_481ad73c:

    # "When I'm finished, it is exactly 10 a.m."
    "Cuando termino, son exactamente las 10 de la mañana."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:68
translate spanish day1_f2bae43e:

    # ss "Alright, [bro], let's go!"
    ss "¡Muy bien, [bro], vamos!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:72
translate spanish day1_caf40c4b:

    # "She calls from the front door. I make sure I have everything I need, then rush down the stairs to meet her at the front door."
    "Me llama desde la puerta principal. Me aseguro de que tengo todo lo que necesito y luego bajo corriendo las escaleras para reunirme con ella en la puerta principal."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:73
translate spanish day1_1660493b:

    # pc "Ready!"
    pc "¡Listo!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:76
translate spanish day1_7072f207:

    # "She leads me out to her car, an older model SUV. The interior is messy with empty coffee cups and fast food bags. I sit in the passenger seat and buckle up."
    "Me lleva hasta su coche, un todoterreno de un modelo antiguo. El interior está desordenado, con tazas de café vacías y bolsas de comida rápida. Me siento en el asiento del copiloto y me abrocho el cinturón."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:79
translate spanish day1_365fcfce:

    # pc "This feels weird. "
    pc "Esto me resulta raro. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:80
translate spanish day1_4339758a_1:

    # ss "What? "
    ss "¿Qué? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:81
translate spanish day1_63cbd288:

    # pc "You driving. Remember all the times I had to drive you places when we were growing up? "
    pc "Que tú conduzcas. ¿Te acuerdas de todas las veces que tuve que llevarte a sitios cuando éramos pequeños? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:82
translate spanish day1_722468e6:

    # ss "Yeah, but I'm not a kid anymore. And you're not driving my car. "
    ss "Sí, pero ya no soy un niño. Y tú no conduces mi coche. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:83
translate spanish day1_c9e546cd:

    # pc "I'm just saying it's weird. "
    pc "Solo digo que es raro. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:86
translate spanish day1_4a97b04a:

    # ss "Alright, let's get this show on the road."
    ss "Vale, pongámonos en marcha."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:89
translate spanish day1_a30cda1c:

    # "She backs out without looking into the rearview mirror, then slams down on the brakes, jerking me forward in my seat. "
    "Da marcha atrás sin mirar por el retrovisor y luego pisa el freno a fondo, lo que me hace dar un tirón hacia delante en el asiento. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:92
translate spanish day1_e947ee1f:

    # "She shifts up into drive and then puts the gas pedal to the floor."
    "Cambia a marcha adelante y pisa el acelerador a fondo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:93
translate spanish day1_5c62a101:

    # "I grip the dashboard, holding on for my life as she zooms down the side streets, barely slowing around corners. "
    "Me agarro al salpicadero, aferrándome con todas mis fuerzas mientras ella se lanza a toda velocidad por las calles secundarias, sin apenas reducir la velocidad en las curvas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:94
translate spanish day1_9bfb97be:

    # "It only takes a few minutes to get to the school. "
    "Solo tardamos unos minutos en llegar al instituto. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:99
translate spanish day1_fc69d3c6:

    # ss "The counselor's office is over there. I'm going to the café over there to have a drink and chat with a friend. Just come get me when you're done. "
    ss "La oficina del orientador está por allí. Yo voy a la cafetería de allí a tomar algo y charlar con una amiga. Ven a buscarme cuando hayas terminado. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:100
translate spanish day1_06d3bcbf:

    # pc "Okay, thanks. "
    pc "Vale, gracias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:101
translate spanish day1_bc7ca1a4:

    # ss "And don't take all day either. I have things I want to do later. "
    ss "Y no te pases todo el día tampoco. Tengo cosas que hacer más tarde. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:102
translate spanish day1_f75c9919:

    # pc "I'll try. "
    pc "Lo intentaré. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:105
translate spanish day1_51bf71a6:

    # "I walk through the courtyard towards the administration office that Suzy had pointed to. "
    "Atravesé el patio en dirección a la oficina de administración que Suzy me había señalado. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:106
translate spanish day1_e42a8d36:

    # "The lobby is busy with people. All students looking to register, like me. "
    "El vestíbulo estaba lleno de gente. Todos eran estudiantes que, como yo, venían a matricularse. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:107
translate spanish day1_b72f9460:

    # "I sign in at the front desk, then wait for my turn to talk to a counselor. "
    "Me registré en recepción y esperé mi turno para hablar con un orientador. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:108
translate spanish day1_c607938a:

    # "It takes nearly an hour for my name to be called. The young woman at the front desk leads me down a short hall and knocks on a partially opened door with a nameplate that says Gertrude Spann."
    "Tardan casi una hora en llamarme. La joven de recepción me acompaña por un pasillo corto y llama a una puerta entreabierta en la que hay un letrero con el nombre de Gertrude Spann."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:109
translate spanish day1_793493ec:

    # "Assistant" "The next student is here, Mrs. Spann."
    "Assistant" "Ya está aquí el siguiente estudiante, señora Spann."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:114
translate spanish day1_f67002ce:

    # sc "Thank you. Hello there, you can just call me Gertrude. It's nice to meet you."
    sc "Gracias. Hola, puedes llamarme Gertrude. Encantada de conocerte."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:115
translate spanish day1_6312d9da:

    # "She puts her hand out to shake mine, gripping it firmly for only a second, then sitting back into her chair and motioning for me to sit across from her."
    "Me tiende la mano para estrechármela, la aprieta con firmeza solo un segundo, luego se recuesta en su silla y me hace un gesto para que me siente frente a ella."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:118
translate spanish day1_d1a3cf1a:

    # "The assistant quickly walks back towards the front desk to help the next student in line. "
    "La asistente se dirige rápidamente hacia la recepción para atender al siguiente estudiante de la cola. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:119
translate spanish day1_0d80bf66:

    # sc "So what are we doing today? "
    sc "¿Qué vamos a hacer hoy? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:120
translate spanish day1_285035ca:

    # pc "I need to register. I've been going to a college in Brazil for the last three years, but I want to transfer here to finish my degree. "
    pc "Necesito matricularme. He estado estudiando en una universidad de Brasil durante los últimos tres años, pero quiero cambiarme aquí para terminar mi carrera. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:122
translate spanish day1_371df839:

    # sc "Brazil? Wow! What were you going to school there for? "
    sc "¿Brasil? ¡Vaya! ¿Qué estudiabas allí? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:123
translate spanish day1_75cc0f72:

    # pc "I had a full scholarship studying quantum physics. "
    pc "Tenía una beca completa para estudiar física cuántica. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:124
translate spanish day1_f5dc9bb8:

    # sc "That's amazing! What happened? Why didn't you finish your degree there, if you don't mind me asking? "
    sc "¡Es increíble! ¿Qué pasó? ¿Por qué no terminaste la carrera allí, si no te importa que te lo pregunte? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:125
translate spanish day1_36677773:

    # pc "I came home to help with my family. My dad went missing a few weeks ago and we're trying to find him. I felt like I needed to come home."
    pc "Volví a casa para ayudar a mi familia. Mi padre desapareció hace unas semanas y estamos intentando encontrarlo. Sentí que tenía que volver a casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:127
translate spanish day1_349dc86a:

    # sc "Oh, I understand. I hope you find your dad, that's awful. "
    sc "Oh, lo entiendo. Espero que encuentres a tu padre, es horrible. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:128
translate spanish day1_92507930:

    # pc "Thank you. "
    pc "Gracias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:130
translate spanish day1_b1340b73:

    # sc "Okay, so you want to finish your degree here. I'm assuming a BS in Physics first, then we'll look at the Masters and Doctorate programs afterwards. "
    sc "Vale, así que quieres terminar tu carrera aquí. Supongo que primero una licenciatura en Física, y después veremos los programas de máster y doctorado. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:131
translate spanish day1_e9630f89:

    # sc "You said you took three years in Brazil. Do you have the official transcripts? "
    sc "Dijiste que estuviste tres años en Brasil. ¿Tienes los expedientes académicos oficiales? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:132
translate spanish day1_68b34aac:

    # pc "Yes, I brought them with me. "
    pc "Sí, los he traído conmigo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:133
translate spanish day1_68acff9f:

    # "I hand her the transcripts and she looks them over with a frown on her face."
    "Le entrego los expedientes académicos y ella los revisa con el ceño fruncido."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:135
translate spanish day1_f65849f0:

    # sc "Okay, okay. Yeah, these look good, but you're missing a couple of basic education courses. "
    sc "Vale, vale. Sí, estos parecen estar bien, pero te faltan un par de asignaturas de formación básica. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:136
translate spanish day1_cb515ed6:

    # pc "Basic education? "
    pc "¿Formación básica? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:138
translate spanish day1_aebbf4f9:

    # sc "Yes, for your degree, you're required to have one semester in English and one in Social Studies. You don't have those here. "
    sc "Sí, para tu título, se requiere que hayas cursado un semestre de inglés y otro de ciencias sociales. Aquí no los tienes. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:139
translate spanish day1_fad16ea5:

    # pc "It wasn't required at my other college. We were completely focused on Science. "
    pc "En mi otra universidad no eran obligatorias. Nos centrábamos completamente en las ciencias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:140
translate spanish day1_9b9e7d7e:

    # sc "That makes sense, but you'll have to take them here. You'll be close to having your BS after taking them though, since you've already taken some of the more intense Science classes. "
    sc "Tiene sentido, pero aquí tendrás que cursarlas. Aunque, una vez las hayas cursado, estarás a punto de obtener tu licenciatura, ya que ya has cursado algunas de las asignaturas de ciencias más intensas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:141
translate spanish day1_833a138b:

    # sc "Do you want to take a full course load? If you do, I can probably easily get you into a scholarship program considering your current situation. "
    sc "¿Quieres cursar la carga lectiva completa? Si es así, probablemente pueda conseguirte fácilmente una beca teniendo en cuenta tu situación actual. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:142
translate spanish day1_ae785278:

    # "A full course load would be a lot of work, but I need to get it done. Plus, I don't have the money to pay for college on my own. I need a scholarship of some sort. "
    "Una carga lectiva completa supondría mucho trabajo, pero tengo que hacerlo. Además, no tengo dinero para pagarme la universidad por mi cuenta. Necesito algún tipo de beca. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:143
translate spanish day1_2289f1ba:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do that. "
    pc "Sí, hagámoslo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:144
translate spanish day1_fcf730d7:

    # sc "Okay, so I'll sign you up for this scholarship. We'll know for sure in a week whether you're qualified or not, but I'm pretty sure you will be fine. "
    sc "Vale, entonces te inscribiré en esta beca. En una semana sabremos con certeza si cumples los requisitos o no, pero estoy bastante seguro de que no tendrás ningún problema. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:145
translate spanish day1_a28b07e0:

    # sc "And I'm going to register you for your classes – you'll take English and Social Studies, along with the rest of the science classes that you need. You should be good to graduate by the end of the semester."
    sc "Y te voy a matricular en tus clases: cursarás Inglés y Ciencias Sociales, junto con el resto de las asignaturas de ciencias que necesitas. Deberías poder graduarte a finales de semestre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:146
translate spanish day1_23804ef9:

    # sc "It's a big course load, but most people don't have any problem with these classes. I think with your previous experience and obvious intellect, you will be fine. "
    sc "Es mucha carga lectiva, pero a la mayoría de la gente no le supone ningún problema. Creo que con tu experiencia previa y tu evidente inteligencia, no tendrás ningún problema. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:147
translate spanish day1_1704862e:

    # pc "That sounds great. "
    pc "Suena genial. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:148
translate spanish day1_bac5ae79:

    # sc "Let me get your ID and I'll take these transcripts and get started. "
    sc "Dame tu DNI y me llevaré estos expedientes académicos para ponerme manos a la obra. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:150
translate spanish day1_f9ff879e:

    # "I hand her my ID from my wallet, then wait while she types up some things at the computer. "
    "Le entrego mi DNI de la cartera y espero mientras ella teclea algo en el ordenador. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:151
translate spanish day1_cdba79e3:

    # "Then she prints off some pages, has me sign a few places, and hands me a large folder stuffed full of papers. "
    "Luego imprime unas cuantas páginas, me pide que firme en algunos sitios y me entrega una carpeta grande repleta de papeles. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:153
translate spanish day1_bf9053dc:

    # sc "Okay, everything's done. "
    sc "Bien, ya está todo listo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:154
translate spanish day1_60d1bbaf:

    # sc "In your folder there, you'll find your schedule, your course plan, and some more information you might find useful about the school. "
    sc "En esa carpeta encontrarás tu horario, tu plan de estudios y más información sobre la universidad que te puede resultar útil. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:155
translate spanish day1_061a7bd6:

    # sc "Your scholarship is all set up and seems to be good. You just need to show up on Monday ready to go."
    sc "Tu beca ya está tramitada y parece estar en orden. Solo tienes que presentarte el lunes listo para empezar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:156
translate spanish day1_8cadbc6f:

    # pc "Wow, that was easy. Thank you. "
    pc "Vaya, qué fácil ha sido. Gracias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:157
translate spanish day1_a4e55d91:

    # sc "And feel free to come up and chat with me if you ever need anything. Usually the place is not nearly this busy and you shouldn't have to wait long to see me."
    sc "Y no dudes en venir a charlar conmigo si alguna vez necesitas algo. Normalmente el lugar no está tan concurrido y no deberías tener que esperar mucho para verme."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:158
translate spanish day1_b93e3840:

    # sc "It doesn't have to be school related. I'm a counselor and I'm here to help you succeed in any way I can. "
    sc "No tiene por qué ser algo relacionado con la escuela. Soy orientadora y estoy aquí para ayudarte a tener éxito en todo lo que pueda. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:159
translate spanish day1_74f006d8:

    # sc "And good luck finding your dad. I hope everything turns out okay. "
    sc "Y buena suerte con la búsqueda de tu padre. Espero que todo salga bien. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:160
translate spanish day1_514b6719:

    # pc "Thank you so much. "
    pc "Muchas gracias. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:161
translate spanish day1_fb3340fa:

    # "She shakes my hand one more time before I leave and walk back down through the busy lobby and out into the courtyard once again. "
    "Me da la mano una vez más antes de que me vaya y vuelva a atravesar el concurrido vestíbulo para salir al patio una vez más. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:164
translate spanish day1_340e82bc:

    # "I make my way over towards the café that Suzy had pointed towards earlier. "
    "Me dirijo hacia la cafetería que Suzy me había señalado antes. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:165
translate spanish day1_606a8b00:

    # "Through the glass window, I can see Suzy sitting at a table, leaning back with her feet propped up in another chair, staring idly at her telephone screen. "
    "A través del ventanal, puedo ver a Suzy sentada en una mesa, recostada con los pies apoyados en otra silla, mirando distraídamente la pantalla de su teléfono. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:167
translate spanish day1_55c29a9d:

    # "A bell on the door gives a little ring as I walk in. Some students glance up at me from an area to the right where they sit in comfortable looking couches and bean bag chairs, but most pay me no attention. "
    "Una campana en la puerta suena ligeramente cuando entro. Algunos estudiantes me miran desde una zona a la derecha donde están sentados en sofás y pufs que parecen cómodos, pero la mayoría no me presta atención. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:169
translate spanish day1_9a5ad86a:

    # ss "It's about time. I was so BORED, and my phone is almost dead. "
    ss "Ya era hora. Estaba tan ABURRIDA, y mi teléfono está casi sin batería. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:170
translate spanish day1_6b17dfbc:

    # ss "Can we go now? "
    ss "¿Podemos irnos ya? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:171
translate spanish day1_7d3a0bf0:

    # pc "We can go now. "
    pc "Podemos irnos ya. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:172
translate spanish day1_ff13accc:

    # ss "Good, it's almost lunch now and I'm starving! "
    ss "¡Bien, ya casi es la hora de comer y me muero de hambre! "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:173
translate spanish day1_0ce5853a:

    # pc "We just had pancakes a couple of hours ago. "
    pc "Acabamos de comer tortitas hace un par de horas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:174
translate spanish day1_8a30bf9e:

    # ss "So? "
    ss "¿Y qué? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:175
translate spanish day1_560760f8:

    # pc "Nothing. "
    pc "Nada. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:176
translate spanish day1_8be61208:

    # ss "Let's go get some food. You're buying."
    ss "Vamos a por algo de comida. Tú pagas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:177
translate spanish day1_6500736f:

    # pc "I barely have any money. "
    pc "Apenas tengo dinero. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:178
translate spanish day1_0317c80c:

    # ss "You want to go get a phone too, right? "
    ss "¿Quieres ir a comprarte un teléfono también, verdad? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:179
translate spanish day1_c1ea7495:

    # pc "Yeah, I kind of need one. "
    pc "Sí, más o menos lo necesito. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:180
translate spanish day1_0173a82e:

    # ss "And Mom said I had to show you around town too. So you can either buy me lunch, or you can pay for gas. Your choice. "
    ss "Y mamá dijo que también tenía que enseñarte la ciudad. Así que o me invitas a comer, o pagas la gasolina. Tú eliges. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:181
translate spanish day1_896764a5:

    # pc "Fine. But keep it cheap. No steak dinners or anything. "
    pc "Vale. Pero que sea barato. Nada de filetes ni nada por el estilo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:183
translate spanish day1_40f90bfb:

    # ss "Yes! I'm craving Jackson Burger. "
    ss "¡Sí! Me apetece un Jackson Burger. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:184
translate spanish day1_2b80e522:

    # pc "Oh yeah! That place is still open? "
    pc "¡Ah, sí! ¿Ese sitio sigue abierto? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:186
translate spanish day1_7ab998de:

    # ss "Are you kidding? They'll be open forever. Their burgers are the best!"
    ss "¿Bromeas? Estarán abiertos para siempre. ¡Sus hamburguesas son las mejores!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:187
translate spanish day1_b99e638f:

    # "I can't argue with that. We used to eat there all the time when I was growing up. "
    "No puedo discutir eso. Solíamos comer allí todo el tiempo cuando era pequeña. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:188
translate spanish day1_97f399f2:

    # "Every Saturday they have an All-You-Can Eat burger basket. The record holder gets their picture on the wall. I think it was 12 burgers last time I saw. "
    "Todos los sábados tienen una cesta de hamburguesas «come todo lo que puedas». Al que bate el récord le cuelgan la foto en la pared. Creo que la última vez que lo vi eran 12 hamburguesas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:189
translate spanish day1_3dc69b5e:

    # "I can't tell you how many Saturdays I went there and tried to beat the record, but the most burgers I was ever able to eat was five, and I felt horrible for the rest of the day. "
    "No sabría decirte cuántos sábados fui allí e intenté batir el récord, pero lo máximo que conseguí comer fueron cinco, y me sentí fatal el resto del día. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:190
translate spanish day1_05aef9a2:

    # pc "Alright, let's go get some burgers then. "
    pc "Vale, pues vamos a por unas hamburguesas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:192
translate spanish day1_2adf8f01:

    # ss "Yay! "
    ss "¡Sí! "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:196
translate spanish day1_8da109e6:

    # "Jackson Burger hasn't changed a bit. It's exactly like I remembered."
    "Jackson Burger no ha cambiado nada. Es exactamente como lo recordaba."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:199
translate spanish day1_0c024706:

    # "Except for that picture on the wall with the record holder. The whole time I had come here growing up the record was held by Jessie something, at 12 burgers."
    "Excepto por esa foto en la pared con el poseedor del récord. Durante todo el tiempo que vine aquí de pequeña, el récord lo tenía una tal Jessie, con 12 hamburguesas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:200
translate spanish day1_e4077616:

    # "Now it's held by somebody named Brandi, at 14 burgers. 14 burgers? HOW? "
    "Ahora lo ostenta alguien llamada Brandi, con 14 hamburguesas. ¿14 hamburguesas? ¿CÓMO? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:201
translate spanish day1_485f2732:

    # "Judging by the photo taken, I wonder how she could have even fit that many burgers into her stomach. "
    "A juzgar por la foto, me pregunto cómo se le pudieron meter tantas hamburguesas en el estómago. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:202
translate spanish day1_81e701c9:

    # "She isn't very big. Nice pair of tits though. She doesn't look at all like somebody I would expect to have eaten 14 burgers at Jackson Burger. "
    "No es muy grande. Aunque tiene un buen par de tetas. No parece en absoluto alguien de quien esperaría que se hubiera comido 14 hamburguesas en Jackson Burger. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:205
translate spanish day1_a20a9eeb:

    # "Taking orders is the owner himself, Mr. Jackson, who has been running this place since it opened roughly a hundred years ago."
    "El que toma los pedidos es el propio dueño, el Sr. Jackson, que lleva este local desde que abrió hace más o menos cien años."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:206
translate spanish day1_2b0842e3:

    # "He is in his 70's now, but still sharp, funny, and charismatic."
    "Ahora tiene unos 70 años, pero sigue siendo agudo, divertido y carismático."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:208
translate spanish day1_f45be6ca:

    # "I pay for the burgers. The meals are only $5 each, so $10 for the two of us. Such a great deal for these burgers."
    "Pago las hamburguesas. Las comidas solo cuestan 5 dólares cada una, así que 10 dólares para los dos. Una ganga para estas hamburguesas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:209
translate spanish day1_07b857c3:

    # "Suzy and I sit to eat at one of the small booths that seems as if they haven't changed since the 50's."
    "Suzy y yo nos sentamos a comer en una de esas pequeñas mesas que parecen no haber cambiado desde los años 50."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:211
translate spanish day1_d1df107e:

    # ss "So how did registration go? "
    ss "¿Qué tal ha ido la matriculación? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:212
translate spanish day1_1e6bd844:

    # pc "Good. I have to take my basics though. "
    pc "Bien. Aunque tengo que cursar las asignaturas básicas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:213
translate spanish day1_82f14014:

    # ss "You haven't taken your basics? "
    ss "¿No las has cursado? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:214
translate spanish day1_a6e674ff:

    # pc "We didn't have to for the college in Brazil. "
    pc "En la universidad de Brasil no teníamos que hacerlo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:216
translate spanish day1_b3c6d6c8:

    # ss "Oh God, let me see your schedule. I hope we're not in any of the same classes. "
    ss "Dios mío, déjame ver tu horario. Espero que no tengamos ninguna clase en común. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:217
translate spanish day1_c945f9ac:

    # "I hand her the envelope as she wipes her hands on the napkin nearby. "
    "Le entrego el sobre mientras ella se limpia las manos con la servilleta que hay cerca. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:224
translate spanish whatswrongclass_e7684331:

    # ss "Are you kidding? I don't need my [brother] watching over everything I do, getting better grades than me, making me look stupid."
    ss "¿Estás de broma? No necesito que mi [brother] esté pendiente de todo lo que hago, sacando mejores notas que yo, haciéndome quedar en ridículo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:225
translate spanish whatswrongclass_59cc5553:

    # pc "I don't do that."
    pc "Yo no hago eso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:226
translate spanish whatswrongclass_f04715ff:

    # ss "Yes you do. You may not try to do it, but you do it. "
    ss "Sí que lo haces. Puede que no intentes hacerlo, pero lo haces. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:227
translate spanish whatswrongclass_575e20ff:

    # pc "If I do, I'm sorry."
    pc "Si lo hago, lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:228
translate spanish whatswrongclass_a9df77bb:

    # ss "It's okay. I know you don't mean to. I'm just not as smart as you, I get it."
    ss "No pasa nada. Sé que no es tu intención. Simplemente no soy tan inteligente como tú, lo entiendo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:229
translate spanish whatswrongclass_86e4def6:

    # pc "You are smart though."
    pc "Pero tú sí que eres inteligente."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:231
translate spanish whatswrongclass_9b60c241:

    # "She raises an eyebrow at me."
    "Me mira levantando una ceja."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:232
translate spanish whatswrongclass_f5c9934a:

    # ss "Don't be condescending. We both know I'm not as smart as you. I'm okay with that. I just don't need it pointed out in front of everybody every day. "
    ss "No seas condescendiente. Las dos sabemos que no soy tan inteligente como tú. No me importa. Pero no necesito que me lo recuerdes delante de todo el mundo todos los días. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:235
translate spanish hopesoclass_aecb5a13:

    # ss "Right? God, could you imagine?"
    ss "¿Verdad? Dios, ¿te lo imaginas?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:239
translate spanish bulletdodged_3fa2b281:

    # ss "Fortunately though, we ARE in some of the same classes, but not at the same times. Bullet dodged."
    ss "Por suerte, sin embargo, sí que estamos en algunas clases juntos, pero no a la misma hora. Me he librado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:240
translate spanish bulletdodged_df595c4b:

    # "After this we eat mostly in silence."
    "Después de esto, comemos casi en silencio."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:242
translate spanish bulletdodged_60ba3fb6:

    # ss "I'm so damn full. That was delicious."
    ss "Estoy tan llena. Estaba delicioso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:243
translate spanish bulletdodged_ba27ea61:

    # "Back when I was younger, I would polish off two or three burgers every time I came here, but now I don't think I could eat another bite."
    "Cuando era más joven, me zampaba dos o tres hamburguesas cada vez que venía aquí, pero ahora no creo que pudiera comer ni un bocado más."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:244
translate spanish bulletdodged_b89168a2:

    # "When we are both finished, we head back out to the car."
    "Cuando terminamos, volvemos al coche."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:251
translate spanish touroftown_c7f29f2a:

    # ss "Okay, so quick tour of Skyhill, the town we both know and love. You know where our house and the school are, obviously."
    ss "Vale, un recorrido rápido por Skyhill, la ciudad que ambos conocemos y amamos. Ya sabes dónde están nuestra casa y el colegio, obviamente."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:255
translate spanish touroftown_6df7be13:

    # ss "And Jackson Burger, best burgers in town."
    ss "Y Jackson Burger, las mejores hamburguesas de la ciudad."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:257
translate spanish touroftown_02ea2624:

    # ss "Jackson Burger, which we should be eating at right now, is right here. Best burgers in town at a reasonable price that is not too much for you to spend on your [sister]."
    ss "Jackson Burger, donde deberíamos estar comiendo ahora mismo, está justo aquí. Las mejores hamburguesas de la ciudad a un precio razonable que no te supondrá un gran gasto para tu [sister]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:258
translate spanish touroftown_81ebfb9e:

    # ss "Further down the street here, there is the law offices that Mom was talking about. You should stop by there sometime and see about getting a job. "
    ss "Más abajo en esta calle, está el bufete de abogados del que hablaba mamá. Deberías pasarte por allí algún día y ver si te dan trabajo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:261
translate spanish touroftown_d7932580:

    # ss "I've seen a help wanted sign in the window for a long time. Some of my friends said the boss is a bitch, but you're pretty desperate, so you might just have to suck it up and deal with it. "
    ss "Hace tiempo que veo un cartel de «Se busca personal» en el escaparate. Algunos de mis amigos dicen que la jefa es una bruja, pero estás bastante desesperado, así que quizá tengas que aguantarte y lidiar con ello. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:264
translate spanish touroftown_7cde6ffc:

    # ss "Then, over here, there is the shopping center. Everything in the town is here basically, starting with the supermarket."
    ss "Luego, por aquí, está el centro comercial. Básicamente, todo lo que hay en la ciudad está aquí, empezando por el supermercado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:267
translate spanish touroftown_6bb210bb:

    # ss "And here's Java Lava, where I work."
    ss "Y aquí está Java Lava, donde trabajo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:273
translate spanish touroftown_fd1c0391:

    # ss "And that's pretty much it. Small boring town. Nothing ever happens. "
    ss "Y eso es más o menos todo. Un pueblo pequeño y aburrido. Nunca pasa nada. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:274
translate spanish touroftown_ee64d037:

    # pc "Does the Supermarket sell phones?"
    pc "¿Venden teléfonos en el supermercado?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:275
translate spanish touroftown_c3329308:

    # ss "There's a little shop next to it that does. "
    ss "Hay una tiendecita al lado que sí los vende. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:276
translate spanish touroftown_cf36cc17:

    # pc "Could we stop there, and then at the law offices on the way back? "
    pc "¿Podríamos parar allí y luego en el bufete de abogados a la vuelta? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:277
translate spanish touroftown_753956bf:

    # ss "Ugh, I guess. "
    ss "Uf, supongo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:280
translate spanish touroftown_b4452e7a:

    # "She parks at the Supermarket and we walk over to the mobile phone store, where I buy the cheapest phone I can find."
    "Aparca en el supermercado y caminamos hasta la tienda de teléfonos móviles, donde compro el teléfono más barato que encuentro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:372
translate spanish tolawoffices_50a16459:

    # "Then she drives to the law office."
    "Luego conduce hasta el bufete de abogados."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:373
translate spanish tolawoffices_1102de62:

    # ss "I'm staying in the car. Good luck. Don't take too long or I'm going to leave you. "
    ss "Me quedo en el coche. Buena suerte. No tardes mucho o te voy a dejar aquí. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:375
translate spanish tolawoffices_ae6279f3:

    # "I step out and walk up to the door. How am I supposed to know how long this will take? It isn't really something I can control. "
    "Salgo y me acerco a la puerta. ¿Cómo voy a saber cuánto tiempo va a llevar esto? No es algo que pueda controlar. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:376
translate spanish tolawoffices_3d178aaa:

    # "The glass door has “Law Offices of Mills & Gonzales” printed on it in white lettering. Below that, a printed sign is taped on the inside that says HELP WANTED. "
    "La puerta de cristal tiene impreso en letras blancas «Despacho de abogados Mills & Gonzales». Debajo, hay un cartel pegado con cinta adhesiva en el interior que dice «SE BUSCA AYUDA». "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:377
translate spanish tolawoffices_2c3a4b71:

    # "I open the door and walk inside. "
    "Abro la puerta y entro. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:379
translate spanish tolawoffices_810de39d:

    # "The small lobby is decorated with a few potted plants and uncomfortable-looking chairs on the left. "
    "El pequeño vestíbulo está decorado con unas cuantas plantas en macetas y sillas de aspecto incómodo a la izquierda. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:380
translate spanish tolawoffices_ae89c21c:

    # "On the right, a large desk sits empty. "
    "A la derecha, hay un gran escritorio vacío. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:381
translate spanish tolawoffices_84b62af0:

    # "A hallway stretches forward some ways, with doors on both sides. "
    "Un pasillo se extiende hacia delante, con puertas a ambos lados. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:382
translate spanish tolawoffices_c6652712:

    # "The place is empty. Nobody in sight. "
    "El lugar está vacío. No hay nadie a la vista. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:383
translate spanish tolawoffices_4a165571:

    # pc "Hello? "
    pc "¿Hola? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:384
translate spanish tolawoffices_614084c5:

    # "I call out. I hear some rustling coming from down the hallway, and a woman's voice calls back. "
    "Llamo. Oigo un crujido que viene del fondo del pasillo y una voz de mujer me responde. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:385
translate spanish tolawoffices_190db744:

    # "???" "Just a second, I'll be right with you. "
    "???" "Un momento, ahora mismo voy. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:388
translate spanish tolawoffices_1f90e502:

    # "A frazzled young woman rushes out of the second door on the left, her arms full of papers."
    "Una joven agotada sale corriendo por la segunda puerta a la izquierda, con los brazos llenos de papeles."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:389
translate spanish tolawoffices_3f829165:

    # "???" "Can I help you? "
    "???" "¿En qué puedo ayudarle? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:390
translate spanish tolawoffices_81220faf:

    # pc "I'm here about the Help Wanted poster. "
    pc "Vengo por el cartel de «Se busca personal». "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:391
