    # "She looks at me suspiciously. "
    "Me mira con recelo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:505
translate spanish tolawoffices_31bab525:

    # "I reach into her car and take out my bag that has the cell phone in it. "
    "Metí la mano en su coche y saqué mi bolso, donde tenía el móvil. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:506
translate spanish tolawoffices_ed0d368e:

    # pc "Well, I'll see you at home. Thanks again for driving me around today. "
    pc "Bueno, nos vemos en casa. Gracias otra vez por llevarme hoy. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:509
translate spanish tolawoffices_65fdee3e:

    # ss "Hey you still owe me gas money!"
    ss "¡Oye, todavía me debes la gasolina!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:510
translate spanish tolawoffices_e902b56c:

    # pc "Oh yeah, sorry. Will $10 do?"
    pc "Ah, sí, lo siento. ¿Te valen 10 dólares?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:511
translate spanish tolawoffices_87ff94f5:

    # ss "That's fine."
    ss "Está bien."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:513
translate spanish tolawoffices_1b7e7694:

    # "I hand her a ten from the little amount of money I have in my wallet."
    "Le entrego un billete de diez de los pocos que tengo en la cartera."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:514
translate spanish tolawoffices_70e27b89:

    # ss "Alright, see you later."
    ss "Vale, hasta luego."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:517
translate spanish tolawoffices_98bddef0:

    # ss "Yeah, yeah. See you later. "
    ss "Sí, sí. Hasta luego. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:520
translate spanish tolawoffices_afba32b7:

    # "She pulls out quickly and cuts off two people as she drives onto the busy road in front of the law offices. "
    "Arranca rápidamente y se adelanta a dos coches al incorporarse a la concurrida calle frente al bufete de abogados. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:521
translate spanish tolawoffices_3e9feed9:

    # "I walk over to one of the company cars. They both look exactly the same – generic black sedans, a few years old, with slightly tinted windows."
    "Me acerco a uno de los coches de la empresa. Los dos son exactamente iguales: sedanes negros genéricos, de hace unos años, con las lunas ligeramente tintadas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:522
translate spanish tolawoffices_c65d2d31:

    # "I press the unlock button on the key fob and one of the cars beeps. I open the driver's side door and get inside."
    "Pulsé el botón de desbloqueo del mando a distancia y uno de los coches pitó. Abrí la puerta del lado del conductor y me metí dentro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:525
translate spanish tolawoffices_762489ab:

    # "The inside of the car is clean and smells a bit musty as if it hasn't been used for a while."
    "El interior del coche estaba limpio y olía un poco a humedad, como si no se hubiera usado en un tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:526
translate spanish tolawoffices_76a7ccb7:

    # "It is simple and not very flashy, but it will get me around until I can buy a car of my own."
    "Era sencillo y nada llamativo, pero me serviría para desplazarme hasta que pudiera comprarme un coche propio."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:527
translate spanish tolawoffices_07e0ebfc:

    # "Actually, it is probably better than any car that I'd ever owned. I'd only had one car before - an old junker that my dad had gotten me."
    "De hecho, probablemente sea mejor que cualquier coche que haya tenido nunca. Solo había tenido un coche antes: un viejo cacharro que me había conseguido mi padre."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:528
translate spanish tolawoffices_ff0881b6:

    # "It barely ran and needed constant work. I sold it off before going to Brazil. Then down there, I didn't have any form of transportation. I just walked everywhere. "
    "Apenas funcionaba y necesitaba reparaciones constantes. Lo vendí antes de irme a Brasil. Una vez allí, no tenía ningún medio de transporte. Simplemente iba andando a todas partes. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:529
translate spanish tolawoffices_076df576:

    # "The car starts as soon as I turn the key, and once I back out onto the street it drives perfectly fine. It doesn't have much power, but enough to get me from place to place."
    "El coche arranca en cuanto giro la llave y, una vez que salgo a la calle, funciona perfectamente. No tiene mucha potencia, pero sí la suficiente para llevarme de un sitio a otro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:530
translate spanish tolawoffices_61f7e0fb:

    # "I would have taken the job even without the car, but now, not having to rely on somebody else to drive me around is the best feeling. "
    "Habría aceptado el trabajo incluso sin el coche, pero ahora, no tener que depender de nadie para que me lleve de un lado a otro es una sensación maravillosa. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:531
translate spanish tolawoffices_5ba209a0:

    # "It's evening now. I have a little time left to do some things before heading home for the night, and I have the means to go anywhere I want."
    "Ya es de noche. Me queda un poco de tiempo para hacer algunas cosas antes de volver a casa, y tengo los medios para ir a donde quiera."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:532
translate spanish tolawoffices_f228727e:

    # "I suddenly remember the park that I used to play at when I was younger and I wonder what it looks like now."
    "De repente me acuerdo del parque en el que solía jugar cuando era más joven y me pregunto cómo estará ahora."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:533
translate spanish tolawoffices_cfe242e6:

    # "There are plenty of places to go, and I have plenty of time to check out that park later. Where do I want to go NOW?"
    "Hay un montón de sitios a los que ir, y tengo tiempo de sobra para pasarme por ese parque más tarde. ¿A dónde quiero ir AHORA?"

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:219
    old "What's wrong with us being in the same class?"
    new "¿Qué hay de malo en que estemos en la misma clase?"

    # game/Scenes/Prologue/day1.rpy:221
    old "I hope so too. That would be horrible."
    new "Yo también lo espero. Eso sería horrible."

